(9376, 'Orlismart 120mg 10 caps.', 'اورليسمارت 10 كبسولات', '42', '56', 'Orlistat', 'Pharopharma', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Weight loss', '120mg', 'Orlistat is indicated for obesity management including weight loss and weight maintenance when used in combination with calorie reduction in overweight and obese adults; this indication applies to both the prescription formulation of 120 mg[L11130] and the over-the-counter formulation of 60 mg.[L31963] Orlistat in the 120 mg prescription formulation is also indicated to reduce the risk of weight regain following weight loss.[L11130]', '6221094088901', '', 3124, '2024-09-28', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
